{"tid":585713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美中貿易1月逆差360億, 特朗普要求減少10億","createTime":"2018-03-09T02:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T04:59:56.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"896e47bb7b46ced153acaa3af2f8a4252faff70b","tid":585713,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:03:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-deficit-with-china-trump-asked-china-to-reduce-by-1-billion-20180308/4285761.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fus-deficit-with-china-trump-asked-china-to-reduce-by-1-billion-20180308%2F4285761.html&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=dc17f2b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-deficit-with-china-trump-asked-china-to-reduce-by-1-billion-20180308/4285761.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美中貿易1月逆差360億 川普要求減少10億<br />\n2018年3月8日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普星期三表示，他已經要求中國制定一項年度計劃，把美中之間貿易逆差減少10億美元。<br />\n<br />\n川普星期三發推說，&ldquo;我們與中國之間的關係一直很好。我們期待看到他們對此的反饋如何。我們必須馬上行動！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n今年1月美國對中國貿易逆差激增百分之16.7，達到360億美元，這是自從2015年9月以來的最高數字，表明川普的&ldquo;美國優先&rdquo;政策對貿易赤字仍然沒有實質作用。與此同時，美國1月的整體貿易逆差增加到9年多以來的新高，總計為566億美元。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部的統計數字表明，今年1月美國對外貿易逆差比去年12月的539億美元增長百分之5，這是自從2008年10月創下602億美元的逆差數字以來的最大逆差。美國貿易逆差已經連續五個月出現增長。"},{"pid":"aed3210891db29f4278106d3fc2a1f83951bdbc8","tid":585713,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:07:00.000Z","msg":"其實自己唔好買made in China 咪得"},{"pid":"b92d1252862078fd33620f6fad8a77d653d78232","tid":585713,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:08:02.000Z","msg":"祖國崛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb21a6a81aca8276bf2c9d93383a56a81ad1f59","tid":585713,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"